        <updateDate>2006-10-04T21:10:42Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Safer Skies Act of 2006 - Amends federal transportation law to direct the Under Secretary of Transportation for Security to prescribe regulations that permit qualified local law enforcement officers to carry accessible weapons while onboard an aircraft to the same extent and subject to the same limits as federal law enforcement officers are permitted to do so.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
